Place a photo of Terry Davis here named terry.jpg or terry.png.

The app will use it as the main image. Without it, a placeholder face
is drawn programmatically.

Suggested source: search for "Terry Davis TempleOS" — use a public-domain
or fair-use image (e.g., his Wikipedia photo or a screenshot from one of
his videos). Keep it square-ish (400x400 works well).
